exercises.name: Push-ups
exercises.description: Do push-ups with your hands on the ground

exercises.name: Sit-ups
exercises.description: Lie down and sit up, touching your toes

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.description: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and squat down

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.description: Step forward with one leg and bend the knee until the thigh is parallel to the ground

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.description: Hold your body in a straight line from head to toe, supported by your forearms and toes

exercises.name: Bench Press
exercises.description: Lay flat on a bench and push a barbell away from your chest

exercises.name: Deadlift
exercises.description: Lift a barbell from the ground to your hips

exercises.name: Overhead Press
exercises.description: Lift a barbell from your shoulders to above your head

exercises.name: Bent Over Rows
exercises.description: Bend over with a barbell in your hands and pull the bar towards your chest

exercises.name: Barbell Curls
exercises.description: Hold a barbell with your hands and curl it towards your chest

exercises.name: Tricep Extensions
exercises.description: Hold a barbell behind your head with your arms extended and then bend your elbows to lower the bar

exercises.name: Dumbbell Flys
exercises.description: Lie on a bench with dumbbells in your hands and raise your arms out to the side

exercises.name: Leg Press
exercises.description: Push weights away from your body using a machine

exercises.name: Calf Raises
exercises.description: Use a machine to raise and lower weights with your feet
